---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/sections/Navbar.astro';
import MenuDrawer from '../../components/sections/MenuDrawer.astro';
import CityPickerDialog from '../../components/sections/CityPickerDialog.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/sections/Footer.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../components/atoms/Breadcrumb.astro';

const url = Astro.url.toString();
const schemaLD = [
  {
    '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
    itemListElement: [
      { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://japanauto.ca/' },
      { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Terms of Use', item: url },
    ],
  },
  {
    '@type': 'WebPage',
    '@id': `${url}#page`,
    name: 'Terms of Use — japanauto.ca',
    description: 'The terms governing use of japanauto.ca by visitors and dealers.',
    url,
    inLanguage: 'en-CA',
    publisher: { '@id': 'https://japanauto.ca/#organization' },
  },
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use — japanauto.ca"
  description="The terms governing use of japanauto.ca by visitors and dealers — a Calgary-based marketplace for used Japanese cars and salvage-yard parts."
  canonical={url}
  schemaLD={schemaLD}
>
  <Navbar slot="navbar" />
  <MenuDrawer slot="menu-drawer" />
  <CityPickerDialog slot="city-picker" />
  <Footer slot="footer" />

  <Breadcrumb
    items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Terms of Use' },
    ]}
  />

  <article class="section" style="padding-top:8px;max-width:720px">
    <h1 class="t-display-l" style="font-size:30px;line-height:38px;margin-bottom:16px">Terms of Use</h1>

    <p class="t-body-m ink-muted" style="font-size:14px;line-height:22px;margin-bottom:14px">
      Effective 5 July 2026.
    </p>

    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      These Terms of Use govern your access to and use of japanauto.ca (the &#39;Site&#39;), a Canadian
      online marketplace for used Japanese vehicles and salvage-yard parts based in Calgary, Alberta
      and operated by NeuroDealer (the &#39;Company&#39;, &#39;we&#39;, &#39;us&#39;). By accessing the Site, browsing
      listings, or creating an account, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree,
      please do not use the Site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">1. Who we are</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      japanauto.ca is a marketplace and listings aggregator. We provide a platform where dealers,
      salvage yards, and private sellers can advertise vehicles and parts to buyers in Toronto,
      Montreal, Vancouver, Calgary, Edmonton, and Ottawa. We are not the seller of any vehicle or
      part listed on the Site, we do not take title to any item, and we are not a party to any
      transaction between a buyer and a seller. Each seller is solely responsible for its own
      listings, the accuracy of the information in them, the condition and legality of the items it
      advertises, and the completion of any sale.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">2. Eligibility</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      You must be at least 18 years of age and resident in Canada to create an account or transact
      through sellers found on the Site. By using the Site you represent that you meet these
      requirements and that any information you provide is accurate and current.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">3. Dealer and seller accounts</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      Sellers may create Free or Pro accounts; new accounts begin with a 30-day trial. If you post
      listings, you agree that every listing will be accurate, complete, and not misleading, and
      that you hold the right to sell the items you advertise. Compliance with all applicable
      dealer-licensing and consumer-protection law — including AMVIC registration in Alberta, OMVIC
      registration in Ontario, and the equivalent regime in any other province — is your
      responsibility, not ours. You must not misrepresent a vehicle&#39;s history, title status,
      mileage, damage, or condition. We may, at our discretion and without notice, decline, edit,
      suspend, or remove any listing or account that we believe violates these Terms, applicable
      law, or the integrity of the marketplace.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">4. Acceptable use</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      You agree not to: scrape, crawl, harvest, or bulk-copy content or data from the Site by any
      automated means without our prior written consent; post fraudulent, deceptive, or unlawful
      listings or content; impersonate any person or entity; interfere with or attempt to gain
      unauthorized access to the Site, its accounts, or its infrastructure; or use the Site for any
      purpose that is illegal or that infringes the rights of others. We may investigate and take
      appropriate action, including account termination and referral to authorities, against
      conduct we consider a violation.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">5. Intellectual property</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      The Site, including its design, text, editorial content, logos, and software, is owned by the
      Company or its licensors and is protected by Canadian and international intellectual-property
      law. You may view and use the Site for your own personal or internal business purposes but may
      not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from it without permission. Sellers
      retain ownership of the listing content and images they submit but grant us a non-exclusive,
      royalty-free licence to host, display, and promote that content on and in connection with the
      Site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">6. Listings are informational</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      Listings, prices, specifications, and any editorial guides on the Site are provided for
      information only. Nothing on the Site is an offer, a promise, or a warranty by us that any
      vehicle or part is available, accurately described, roadworthy, or fit for a particular
      purpose. Availability and terms are set by the seller and may change without notice.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">7. Disclaimers and limitation of liability</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      The Site is provided on an &#39;as is&#39; and &#39;as available&#39; basis. To the fullest extent permitted
      by law, we disclaim all warranties, express or implied, including warranties of
      merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement. Vehicles and parts
      are sold by third parties; before you buy, you are responsible for independently verifying the
      VIN, ownership, lien status, accident and title history, and mechanical condition of any item,
      and we strongly recommend an independent inspection and a title/lien search. To the fullest
      extent permitted by law, the Company is not liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or
      consequential damages, or for any loss arising out of a transaction between you and a seller,
      the condition of any vehicle or part, or your use of or inability to use the Site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">8. Indemnity</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      You agree to indemnify and hold harmless the Company and its officers, employees, and agents
      from any claim, loss, liability, or expense (including reasonable legal fees) arising out of
      your listings, your use of the Site, your breach of these Terms, or your violation of any law
      or third-party right.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">9. Governing law</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      These Terms are governed by the laws of the Province of Alberta and the federal laws of Canada
      applicable there, without regard to conflict-of-laws principles. You agree to the exclusive
      jurisdiction of the courts of Alberta for any dispute arising out of these Terms or your use
      of the Site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">10. Changes to these Terms</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      We may update these Terms from time to time. When we do, we will revise the effective date at
      the top of this page. Your continued use of the Site after a change takes effect constitutes
      acceptance of the revised Terms.
    </p>

    <h2 class="t-h-l" style="font-size:20px;line-height:28px;margin:24px 0 10px">11. Contact</h2>
    <p class="t-body-m" style="font-size:15px;line-height:23px;margin-bottom:14px">
      Questions about these Terms — <a href="mailto:support@japanauto.ca" style="color:var(--color-ink-strong);text-decoration:underline">support@japanauto.ca</a>
      or 1-833-527-2622.
    </p>

    <p class="t-body-m ink-muted" style="font-size:14px;line-height:22px;margin-top:24px">
      Note: this is a standard template and is pending review by Canadian legal counsel before we
      onboard paying customers. It does not constitute legal advice.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
